#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/bitacora.html:51
msgid ""
"Todo lo que las sillas por API key hacen sobre <strong>esta máquina</strong> queda acá.\n"
"        Las <strong>lecturas</strong> (inspect, read_file, system_report) se ejecutan solas; las\n"
"        <strong>mutaciones</strong> (apply_fix) esperan tu aprobación y nunca corren sin tu OK."
msgstr ""
"Everything API-key seats do on <strong>this machine</strong> lands here. "
"<strong>Reads</strong> (inspect, read_file, system_report) run on their own;"
" <strong>mutations</strong> (apply_fix) wait for your approval and never run"
" without your OK."

