msgid "Toolbelt"
msgstr "Toolbelt"

#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/conexiones.html:108
msgid ""
"El login de cada CLI vive en <strong>tu terminal</strong>, no acá: Swarm solo detecta si el\n"
"            archivo de credenciales <strong>existe</strong> (nunca lo lee ni lo muestra) y el runner lo monta\n"
"            solo-lectura en contenedores descartables."
msgstr ""
"Each CLI’s login lives in <strong>your terminal</strong>, not here: Swarm "
"only detects whether the credentials file <strong>exists</strong> (it never "
"reads nor shows it) and the runner mounts it read-only in throwaway "
"containers."

#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/conexiones.html:111
msgid "Logueá el CLI en el host y encendé su silla en"
msgstr "Log the CLI in on the host and turn on its seat in"

#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/conexiones.html:122
msgid "Detectado"
msgstr "Detected"

#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/conexiones.html:122
msgid "No detectado"
msgstr "Not detected"

#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/conexiones.html:128
msgid "Para conectarlo, en tu terminal:"
msgstr "To connect it, in your terminal:"

#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/conexiones.html:137
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Chequeado por el worker al arrancar (%(chequeado_at)s). Si te acabás de loguear,\n"
"            reiniciá el worker (♻️ en Sillas) para rechequear."
msgstr ""
"Checked by the worker at startup (%(chequeado_at)s). If you just logged in, "
"restart the worker (♻️ in Seats) to re-check."

#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/conexiones.html:140
msgid "Chequeado en vivo (modo dev, sin worker dockerizado)."
msgstr "Checked live (dev mode, no dockerized worker)."

#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/conexiones.html:148
msgid ""
"Las sillas por <strong>API key</strong> (Anthropic / OpenAI-compatible / OpenRouter / Gemini)\n"
"            hablan directo con el proveedor, sin CLI. Las keys se guardan <strong>cifradas con tu\n"
"            passphrase</strong> en <code>data/secrets.enc</code>: si se pierde el pendrive sin la passphrase,\n"
"            no hay tokens en claro."
msgstr ""
"Seats by <strong>API key</strong> (Anthropic / OpenAI-compatible / "
"OpenRouter / Gemini) talk straight to the provider, no CLI. Keys are stored "
"<strong>encrypted with your passphrase</strong> in "
"<code>data/secrets.enc</code>: if the stick is lost without the passphrase, "
"there are no plaintext tokens."

#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/conexiones.html:165
msgid "Desbloquear"
msgstr "Unlock"

#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/conexiones.html:166
msgid "Bloquear"
msgstr "Lock"

#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/conexiones.html:171
msgid ""
"Pegá tu primera key abajo y tocá Guardar — queda creada y activa en un solo "
"paso."
msgstr ""
"Paste your first key below and hit Save — it’s created and active in a "
"single step."

#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/conexiones.html:181
#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/conexiones.html:319
msgid "Configurada"
msgstr "Configured"

#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/conexiones.html:181
