#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/sillas.html:103
#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/sillas.html:166
msgid "Quitar"
msgstr "Remove"

#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/conexiones.html:196
msgid ""
"La passphrase nunca se guarda ni se loguea; se usa solo para cifrar y "
"descifrar tus keys."
msgstr ""
"The passphrase is never stored nor logged; it’s only used to encrypt and "
"decrypt your keys."

#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/conexiones.html:204
msgid ""
"Con el toolbelt <strong>encendido</strong>, las sillas por API key dejan de solo conversar\n"
"            y pueden <strong>inspeccionar y operar la computadora donde corre Swarm</strong> (la del cliente). Es el\n"
"            corazón del soporte: la silla mira el sistema <strong>real</strong> en vez de adivinar."
msgstr ""
"With the toolbelt <strong>on</strong>, API-key seats stop just chatting and "
"can <strong>inspect and operate the computer where Swarm runs</strong> (the "
"client’s). It’s the heart of support work: the seat looks at the "
"<strong>real</strong> system instead of guessing."

#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/conexiones.html:212
#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/conexiones.html:385
msgid "Toolbelt encendido"
msgstr "Toolbelt on"

#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/conexiones.html:212
#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/conexiones.html:385
msgid "Toolbelt apagado"
msgstr "Toolbelt off"

#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/conexiones.html:214
msgid ""
"Forzado por SWARM_TOOLBELT en el launcher — se controla desde ahí, no acá."
msgstr ""
"Forced by SWARM_TOOLBELT in the launcher — it’s controlled from there, not "
"here."

#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/conexiones.html:215
#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/conexiones.html:386
msgid "Las sillas API pueden operar esta máquina."
msgstr "API seats can operate this machine."

#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/conexiones.html:216
#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/conexiones.html:387
msgid "Las sillas API solo conversan; no ven la máquina."
msgstr "API seats only chat; they can’t see the machine."

#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/conexiones.html:219
msgid "Encender / apagar el toolbelt"
msgstr "Turn the toolbelt on / off"

#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/conexiones.html:228
msgid ""
"<strong>Lectura automática:</strong> ver el SO, procesos, disco, archivos y comandos de\n"
"                <strong>solo lectura</strong> (allowlist por sistema) — sin pedir permiso, para diagnosticar rápido."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Automatic reads:</strong> see the OS, processes, disk, files and "
"<strong>read-only</strong> commands (per-system allowlist) — no permission "
"asked, for quick diagnosis."

#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/conexiones.html:231
msgid ""
"<strong>Cambios con tu OK:</strong> instalar, editar o reiniciar algo queda <strong>pendiente</strong>\n"
"                en la Bitácora de la mesa hasta que vos lo apruebes. <strong>Nunca se ejecuta solo.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Changes with your OK:</strong> installing, editing or restarting "
"something stays <strong>pending</strong> in the table’s Logbook until you "
"approve it. <strong>It never runs on its own.</strong>"

#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/conexiones.html:234
msgid ""
"<strong>Todo queda registrado</strong> en la Bitácora de cada mesa (lecturas"
" y cambios)."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Everything is recorded</strong> in each table’s Logbook (reads and "
"changes)."

#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/conexiones.html:238
msgid ""
"Apagado por defecto. Necesita una silla por API key con un modelo que soporte\n"
"            <strong>herramientas</strong> (function-calling); si el modelo no las soporta, la silla las ignora.\n"
"            Pedile <code>system_report</code> para probar."
msgstr ""
"Off by default. Needs an API-key seat with a model that supports "
"<strong>tools</strong> (function-calling); if the model doesn’t, the seat "
"ignores them. Ask it for <code>system_report</code> to try."

